entry.title: Zelensky Visits Recaptured City, Calls for More Help From Allies
entry.content: In visiting the retaken areas, the president is seeking to capitalize on the country’s battlefield gains, which Ukrainian officials hope will help encourage its Western backers to send more military and financial aid.

entry.title: Royal Family Will Unite to Accompany Queen's Coffin Through London
entry.content: The royal family will unite in procession to move Queen Elizabeth II’s coffin from Buckingham Palace to Westminster Hall in London, where it will lie in state for four days before her official funeral.
